text: 4 saal beet gye tumhare saath, but I am still confused what are you! 1st year mae you were the person who wanted to achieve so much. 2nd year mae tum kabhi dikhe hi nhi. Uske baad see to bas kisi bhi room me masti ho rahi have, matlab saini waha hoga. Tu modi, aur mae amit. Bda mza aaya the among us me. Abb toh geoguessr aur skribblr have apni zindagi me.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Okay, abb likne ka time aa gya hae, tere baare me. This is going to be tough, kyunki jab itni saari memories ho toh, kya likhu yaad nhi aata. Joh bhi ho, mere down time par tum hamesha the. 1st year me exam ke time teri books churane ka alag hi swad tha. Mae saara time toh tere ya Archies ke room me pda rehta tha. Teri ek baat joh hamesha yaad rahegi, woh hae PJs. Sorry mene kabhi tujhe branch change ke liye congrats nhi kiya. Abb tujhe contact me rehne ke liye toh nhi kahunga, kyuki mae kabhi terese door toh hone hi nhi wala.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Hello Brother. Kaise ho? Hmari dosti ko 5 saal ho gye. Allen se kahani start hoti hae, IITK mae aana jana tumhare saath. DOPA ki POR resume me likh raho ho kya? Suna hae aajkal hair dye karwaye hae, kya chakar hae? Hope, ki jald ek saath ho.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Kaise bhaiya kaise. Padhai me topper aur masti mae bhi. CGS ka course tumhare karn hua hae bhai. Systems ke courses se tumhe kitna pyaar hae yaar. Tumne duniya ki har cheez experience kar rakhi hae(sunne me toh yeh hi aaya hae). Woh din yaad hae 1st year ke, hall ki solar panels par tum mae aur barwal horror stories share kar rahe the. Aleena ko meri taraf se hi kehna.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Thanks mere Bhai, padhane ke liye. Tumhe karn hi degree complete ho payi meri, aur kafhi aur logo ki. Manali wali trip toh hamesha yaad rahegi. All the best for your future endevours. And send me your location everything you shift from one continent to another.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Bade bhaiya. Bda mast khelte ho yarr. Mujay volleyball me mujay tricks seekhane ke liye. Mafia kehlene ka mza tere bina nhi aata yrr, ek baar beech me se naraz ho gye the, bohat bura lga tha. ROS software seek na paye hum dono. Kabhi doobara uthane ka mnn ho toh btana. Aur Andrew NG ke notes bohat sexy bnae the tumhe.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Thank God, you exist. You are my 3am philosophical talks wala person. And man we seriously need to discuss, does Raghav exist or not :)
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Sir. Aryanc403. Coding grandmaster. Thanks yaar coding sekhane ke liye. It was a long journey admiring you, and trying to achieve 1900 rating while learning from you.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Bhai Bhai. Kya bakchod aadmi hae yarr. Bohat maze maare hae apan ne ek saath. Har 2 hafte mae Z-square maal jakar movie dekh aate the. Itne assignments ki hera pheri ki hae. Woh among us ke matches jisme pehli hi turn mae tumhe nikal dete the. Tujhe na bhool payenge.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Kaise hooooo? Aare bohat energy wale bande ho yarr. 1st yr me SOC ke time, tumhara blind logo ke Infrasenstive glasses ka idea hamesha yaad rahega. Also thanks a lot man, gym me mujay guide karne ke liye. Tumhara karn mae kafhi motivate hua tha, regular gyming ke liye. Hope, jald mulakat ho
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text:
RICKY TICKY TACKY BIIICH - Probably Pickle Rick
Ek baat btao, hmari dosti hui kaise thi. SOC ke time? Techkriti ke hackathon ke time? KD ki labs me? Assignment ke time? Grade sheet lene ke time? Ya abhi donut ke time? No matter kaise dost bane, but dost bohat sahi ho yarr. Mano na mano instagram par best status tumhare hote hae. And mnn kare toh donut complete karna.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Ishu bhai kaise ho? 1st year mae bhi baate hui thi apni. Yaad hae FIFA. Tum bohat ziada football mae interested the. Kabhi yaad aaye toh bindaas call ya message kar dena.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Bro, woh kya din the. Apni pizza parties. Hum charo ki pubg, and tumhare SPO ke kisse. Bro jaha kahi bhi ho, contact me rehna. Aur ek aur baat, raat ko among us kheloge?
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Hello roomie. Bhai 1st year mae bluff khelte khelte tum magician ban gaye. Ek baat joh tumhari mae hamesha adore karta rahonga, was your dedication to athletics. Bakchodi karne ke liye tum best insaan ho bhai, inborn tolent hae. Aur time hona chahiye tha yaar, bakchodi karne ke liye.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Thanks bro, itni jolly personality ke liye. Like aase bohat kam log hote hae, joh knowledge ko fun way me bta sakte hae, aur yeh quality tumme hae. Just love that man. Humne kis hackathon me part nhi liya. Google hash. Okta hackathon, Mimic ki organisation banai. Nightouts par nightouts. All the best bro, milte rahenge.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Delhi se hae ***. A gentleman kisses and never tells. Standup artist hoon bro. Yeh sab iconic lines aur kiski ho sakti hae. Zomato se tum joh pizza hacks karte the, ussi ko interview me mene btaya, and woh khush ho gye, mere insights se. Isske liye thanks yrr. All the best Bro, for your future endeavors.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Nice bio. Abb video ne sab kuch bta hi diya hae, kuch btane ke lilye bcha nhi. But ek baat jo video mae nhi thi, woh thi tumhare khaane ki speed. Meri wing me mae slow khata tha, toh mujay company ke liye tum mil jate the. Bakchodi karne ke liye hamesha tayar rehte hae, all the best for that in future.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Wow, bahut great personality ho bhai. Bohat memories hae apni sahi me. Film club se start kiya, freshers video bna kar. Galaxy me I.T. ka spoof bnaya. Odessey me bunk. Types of intelligence par charche. Thanks for the formal shoes during internship season. Thanks for teaching BSBE??? (sorry course ka number bhi bhool gya hoon, jisme genetics tha upar upar se). And last but not the least, thanks for recommending Solo Leveling. Bohat epic cheez hae. And just abhi alga chapter aaya hae. Wohi padne lga. See ya
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: I am really sorry I didn't recognize you in SOC481. But NLP ke through finally hmari mulakaat ho hi gyi. Bechaare Abhisekh ne bohat mehnat ki hae uss course me. Hope we cross paths again in life.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Bro, kya discussions ki hae apan ne. Canteen mae spin the bottle, oat mae bday tumhara. Adventure club ke kisse ho, ya senate ki koi baat, sab share kiye hae tumne mere saath. Covid na hota toh we would be gymmates and quash champions by now. Jahan bhi hoge future me, jab bhi duniya badle ka mnn ho, mujay call kar dena.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Bhai bhai, yaad rakhio sword art online mae joh nerve gear tha, woh hum aslimat me ek saath bnayenge. Bhoolna mat.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: B5 ka tempo high hae. Bhai TA101 me saari raat ek saath marwate the. Best wishes for you IAS journey.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Snehal bhai, 3rd row 2nd seat from corner in KD lab. This seat will always have your name inscribed on it. Hum mile PE101 me the, weirdest place to start a friendship. And uske baad DSA ki shuruwat tumne karwai thi. Thanks a lot for that. Kahi par bhi ho contact me rehna
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Meow. Singing sensation, konsi series dekh rahe ho? Tumhara favorite gaming name, John Wick kyu tha? And please yaar ek baar aur, give me some sunshine, guitar par suna do.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Hello bhai, Kya haal hae?
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Steve Jobs, lets write your biography. Tumhare saath bohat masti ki hae. Mama Mio ka oreo shake and Kathi roll, were our reward for working late nights. You are the one who wants to solve the problems of our world. Never lose that, bcz that's your virtue I adore
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Most of the time toh mae tumhare room mae hota tha. Itna sab kuch kiya hae uss room mae. Saari assignments, tumhari favorite sting, apni Manali ki itinerary, and what not. Yeh memoir likne ke baad, tumse meet par milne aa raha hoon ;)
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text:
The results others see :-  valorant
The struggle they don't :- fortnite, overwatch, borderlands.

Thanks for getting me in anime and for teaching me how to chillax

text: Aur bhai, kaise ho? Hum dono kabhi bhi planned way me nhi mile. Mae kahi bhi tumhe milta, I was like coincidence. 1st year me Summer of Code, uske baad tutorial building, phir kabhi ccd, end me among us mae Trump ke roop mae mile. All the best Man, tumhare saath baat karte hamesha excited ho jata tha mae.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal

text: Hello Influencer. Thanks for teaching me though the ways of IITK and helping me socialize. Bohat inspired raha hoon mae tumse. Hope we work on some projects soon.
author: Sudhanshu  Bansal
